<br>
3-4 mages in a group.<br>
<br>
Pull 2-3 mobs<br>
<br>
put a pet on each. give them a second to get decent agro.<br>
<br>
Each mage casts scirocco.<br>
<br>
Ka-Boom.<br>
<br>
You can hit more than 4 mobs btw.  Scirocco is my NPC pet killer.<br>
<br>
Pulling 3 Shadowknights in Chardok with their pets.  Got 6 mobs grouped togeter. 3 mobs 3 pets.<br>
<br>
Scirocco will kill the 3 pets AND will hit the 3 NPC Shadowknights AND you'll have a 2nd wave that hits 1 of the npc shad knights.<br>
<br>
It has to do with a wave killing the NPC PET not counting towards the 4 hit total.<br>
