<br>
You deliver a critical strike (900).<br>
You have hit a &lt;name of mob&gt; for 900 points of non-melee damage.<br>
You deliver a critical strike (900).<br>
You have hit a &lt;name of mob&gt; for 900 points of non-melee damage.<br>
You deliver a critical strike (900).<br>
You have hit a &lt;name of mob&gt; for 900 points of non-melee damage.<br>
<br>
Potential 2700 damage for one shot of manastorm... but of course criticalling 3 times in a row is ULTRA rare but is possible. The best I've personally done is 2 criticals in a row 900 900 with one shot of manastorm.<br>
<br>
Now if it's 2 mobs and you critical all 4 waves.. that's a potential 900 x 4 = 3600 damage with one shot of manastorm.<br>
